  <name>UpToDate</name>
  <summary>Modern system update manager</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      UpToDate is a modern GNOME application that provides a unified interface
      for updating packages across multiple package managers and systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support for multiple package managers (pacman, apt, dnf, Flatpak, Snap, etc.)</li>
      <li>Real-time progress tracking</li>
      <li>Detailed command output logging</li>
      <li>Dry run support for testing updates</li>
      <li>Custom command support</li>
      <li>Native GNOME interface with libadwaita</li>
      <li>No external dependencies - native implementation</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
